{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "本章写石破天随群雄进入侠客岛石室，众高手尽被《侠客行》图解与注释困住，白自在、温仁厚等人多年争辩不休，却始终不得要领。石破天因不识文字，反只从壁上图形、剑势、云气与蝌蚪纹中体会经脉运行，竟在不知不觉间练成二十三室武学，并于第二十四室《太玄经》蝌蚪图中贯通全身内息，将诸般所学融汇为一。龙木二岛主由此顿悟：真正秘奥不在文字，而在图形线路，注解反是误导。二人既喜且悲，知数十年心愿已了，又恐石破天因神功招祸，命他严守秘密，并毁去石壁图谱、遣散群雄。其后龙木二岛主因心愿得偿兼试掌耗尽真元而逝，石破天含悲随众乘船离岛。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "众位心中尚有什么疑窦，便请直言。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "龙岛主说是邀我们来看古诗图解，那到底是什么东西，便请赐观如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正要求教于各位高明博雅君子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "孙女婿，咱爷儿俩打头阵。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫弟子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洞内有二十四座石室，各位可请随意来去观看，看得厌了，可到洞外散心。一应饮食，每间石室中均有置备，各位随意取用，不必客气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "speaker_name": "丁不四",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "一切都是随意，可客气得很啊。就是不能“随意离岛”，是不是？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_ding_bu_si",
      "text": "丁先生何出此言？各位来到侠客岛是出于自愿，若要离去，又有谁敢强留？海滩边大船小船一应俱全，各位何时意欲归去，尽可自便。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "群雄",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "我们现下就要去了，可不可以？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_qun_xiong",
      "text": "自然可以啊，各位当我和木兄弟是什么人了？我们待客不周，已感惭愧，岂敢强留嘉宾？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "text": "温三兄，你……你……你在这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "speaker_name": "温仁厚",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "怎么到今天才来？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "text": "十年前我听说你让侠客岛邀来喝腊八粥，只道你……只道你早就仙去了，曾大哭了几场，那知道……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "speaker_name": "温仁厚",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "我好端端在这里研习上乘武功，怎么就会死了？可惜，可惜你来得迟了。你瞧，这第一句“赵客缦胡缨”，其中对这个“胡”字的注解说……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "text": "温三兄，这十年来你起居如何？怎地也不带个信到山东家中？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "speaker_name": "温仁厚",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "你说什么？这“侠客行”的古诗图解，包蕴古往今来最最博大精深的武学秘奥，咱们竭尽心智，尚自不能参悟其中十之一二，那里还能分心去理会世上俗事？你看图中此人，绝非燕赵悲歌慷慨的豪杰之士，却何以称之为“赵客”？要解通这一句，自非先明白这重要关键不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "speaker_name": "温仁厚",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "白兄，我最近揣摩而得，图中人儒雅风流，本该是阴柔之象，注解中却说：“须从威猛刚强处着手”，那当然说的是阴柔为体、阳刚为用，这倒不难明白。但如何为“体”，如何为“用”，中间实有极大学问。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "不错。温兄，这是我的孙女婿，你瞧他人品还过得去罢？小子，过来见过温三爷爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "text": "温三爷爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "speaker_name": "温仁厚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好！左阴右阳，阴阳共济，多半是这道理了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "text": "庄子说剑篇云……温兄，“缦胡”二字应当连在一起，“缦胡缨”是说他头上所带之缨并不精致，并非说他带了胡人之缨。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xu_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "白须老者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老弟，你刚才这一剑设想虽奇，但你要记得，这一路剑法的总纲，乃“吴钩霜雪明”五字。吴钩者，弯刀也……直中有曲，曲中有直，方是“吴钩霜雪明”这五字的宗旨。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_xu_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "黑须老者",
      "listener": "char_bai_xu_lao_zhe",
      "text": "大哥，你却忘了另一个要点……这个“佩”字，这个“带”字，才是诗中最要紧的关键所在。吴钩虽是弯刀，却是佩带在身，并非拿出来使用。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xu_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "白须老者",
      "listener": "char_hei_xu_lao_zhe",
      "text": "然而不然。“吴钩霜雪明”，精光闪亮，就非入鞘之吴钩，利器佩带在身而不入鞘，焉有是理？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_lian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑脸汉子",
      "listener": "char_tian_xu_dao_ren",
      "text": "这壁上的注解说道：白居易诗云：“勿轻直折剑，犹胜曲全钩。”可见我这直折之剑，方合石壁注文原意。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_xu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "天虚道人",
      "listener": "char_hei_lian_han_zi",
      "text": "“吴钩霜雪明”是主，“犹胜曲全钩”是宾。喧宾夺主，必非正道。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_zi_yuan_ge",
      "speaker_name": "远哥",
      "listener": "char_nv_zi_qian_mei",
      "text": "总是不对。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_zi_qian_mei",
      "speaker_name": "倩妹",
      "listener": "char_nan_zi_yuan_ge",
      "text": "远哥，比之五个月前，这一招可大有进境了。咱们再想想这一条注解……为什么吴王阖庐的宝刀，与别人的宝刀就有不同？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_zi_yuan_ge",
      "speaker_name": "远哥",
      "listener": "char_nv_zi_qian_mei",
      "text": "吴越春秋云……倩妹，这故事甚是残忍，为了吴王百金之赏，竟杀死了自己的两个儿子。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_zi_qian_mei",
      "speaker_name": "倩妹",
      "listener": "char_nan_zi_yuan_ge",
      "text": "我猜想这“残忍”二字，多半是这一招的要诀，须当下手不留余地，纵然是亲生儿子，也要杀了。否则壁上的注释文字，何以特地注明这一节。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "爷爷，那些字说些什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "speaker_name": "温仁厚",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "错了，错了！白兄，你武功虽高，但我在此间已有十年，难道这十年功夫都是白费的？总有些你没领会到的心得罢？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "text": "武学犹如佛家的禅宗，十年苦参，说不定还不及一夕顿悟。我以为这一句的意思是这样……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_ren_hou",
      "speaker_name": "温仁厚",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "大谬不然。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "爷爷，爷爷！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_cha_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "愚茶道人",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "威德先生，你天授神力，老道甘拜下风。然而咱们比的是剑法，可不是比内力。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_yu_cha_dao_ren",
      "text": "愚茶道长，你剑法比我高明，我是佩服的。但这是你武当派世传的武学，却不是石壁上剑法的本意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_cha_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "愚茶道人",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "依你说却是如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_yu_cha_dao_ren",
      "text": "这一句“吴钩霜雪明”这个“明”字，大有道理……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "爷爷，咱们回去了，好不好？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "这里龙岛主说，咱们什么时候想走，随时可以离去。海滩边有许多船只，咱们可以走了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "胡说八道！为什么这样心急？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "text": "婆婆在那边等你呢，她说要等你三个月，只等到三月初八。倘若三月初八还不见你回去，她便要投海自尽。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_zi_zai",
      "speaker_name": "白自在",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "三月初八？咱们是腊月初八到的，还只过了两三天，日子长着呢，怕什么？慢慢再回去好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yi_ge_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "第一个老者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一首“侠客行”乃大诗人李白所作。但李白是诗仙，却不是剑仙，何以短短一首二十四句的诗中，却含有武学至理？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_er_ge_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "第二个老者",
      "listener": "char_di_yi_ge_lao_zhe",
      "text": "创制这套武功的才是一位震古铄今、不可企及的武学大宗师。他老人家不过借用了李白这首诗，来抒写他的神奇武功。咱们不可太钻牛角尖，拘泥于李白这首“侠客行”的诗意。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_san_ge_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "第三个老者",
      "listener": "char_di_yi_ge_lao_zhe",
      "text": "纪兄之言虽极有理，但这句“银鞍照白马”，如离开了李白的诗意，便不可索解。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yi_ge_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "第一个老者",
      "listener": "char_di_san_ge_lao_zhe",
      "text": "是啊。不但如此，我以为还得和第四室中那句“飒沓如流星”连在一起，方为正解。解释诗文固不可断章取义，咱们研讨武学，也不能断章取义才是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_er_ge_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "第二个老者",
      "listener": "char_di_yi_ge_lao_zhe",
      "text": "你既自负于这两句诗所悟比我为多，为何用到轻功之上，却也不过尔尔，始终追我不上？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yi_ge_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "第一个老者",
      "listener": "char_di_er_ge_lao_zhe",
      "text": "难道你又追得我上了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_lao_zhe_zhi_yi",
      "speaker_name": "老者甲",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "那里来的少年，竟也来学咱们一般奔跑？哈哈，这算什么样子？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_lao_zhe_zhi_er",
      "speaker_name": "老者乙",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "这般的轻功，居然也想来钻研石壁上的武功？嘿嘿！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_lao_zhe_zhi_san",
      "speaker_name": "老者丙",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "人家醉八仙的醉步，那也是自有规范的高明武功，这个小兄弟的醉九仙，可太也滑稽了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ren_zhi_yi",
      "speaker_name": "持兵刃者甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "银光灿烂，鞍自平稳。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ren_zhi_er",
      "speaker_name": "持兵刃者乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“照”者居高而临下，“白”则皎洁而渊深。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ren_zhi_san",
      "speaker_name": "持兵刃者丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天马行空，瞬息万里。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ren_zhi_si",
      "speaker_name": "持兵刃者丁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李商隐文：“手为天马，心为国图。”韵府：“道家以手为天马”，原来天马是手，并非真的是马。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "多承二位岛主款待，又让我见识石壁上的武功，十分感谢。小人今日告辞。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些字怎地如此古怪，看上一眼，便会头晕？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "石帮主注目《太玄经》，原来是位精通蝌蚪文的大方家。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "text": "小人一个字也不识，只是瞧这些小蝌蚪十分好玩，便多看了一会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "这就是了，这部《太玄经》以古蝌蚪文写成，我本来正自奇怪，石帮主年纪轻轻，居然有此奇才，识得这等古奥文字。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "text": "那我不看了，不敢打扰两位岛主。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "你不用去，尽管在这里看便是，也打扰不了咱们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妙极！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "果然妙极！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "果然妙极！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "小人不分轻重的胡闹，请两位见谅。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "石帮主天纵奇才，可喜可贺，受我一拜。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "两位如此……这个……客气，这……这可折杀小人了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "石帮主……请……请起……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 485
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "两位怎么了？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "石帮主，我兄弟闷在心中数十年的大疑团，得你今日解破，我兄弟委实感激不尽。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 503,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "我怎地……怎地解破了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "石帮主何必如此谦光？你参透了这首“侠客行”的石壁图谱，不但是当世武林中的第一人……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "小人不敢，小人不敢。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 511,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "这石壁上的蝌蚪古文，在下与木兄弟所识得的还不到一成，不知石帮主肯赐予指教么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 513,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "我跟两位说知便是。我看这条蝌蚪时，“中注穴”中便有跳动；再看这条蝌蚪，“太赫穴”便大跳一下……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "我说错了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "原来……原来……石帮主看的是一条条……一条条那个蝌蚪，不是看一个个字，那么石帮主如何能通解全篇《太玄经》？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "小人自幼没读过书，当真是一字不识，惭愧得紧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "你不识字？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "你不识字？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "不识字。我……我回去之后，定要阿绣教我识字，否则人人都识字，我却不识得，给人笑话，多不好意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "你既不识字，那么自第一室至第二十三室，壁上这许许多多注释，却是谁解给你听的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 539,
      "line_end": 541
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "没人解给我听。白爷爷解了几句，关东那位范大爷解了几句，我也不懂，没听下去。我……我只是瞧着图形，胡思乱想，忽然之间，图上的云头或是小剑什么的，就和身体内的热气连在一起了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 541,
      "line_end": 547
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "你不识字，却能解通图谱，这……这如何能够？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 549,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "text": "难道冥冥中真有天意？还是这位石帮主真有天纵奇才？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 551,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "我懂了，我懂了。大哥，原来如此！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 555,
      "line_end": 557
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "石帮主，幸亏你不识字，才得解破这个大疑团，令我兄弟死得瞑目，不致抱恨而终。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 563,
      "line_end": 565
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "什么……什么死得瞑目？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 567,
      "line_end": 567
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "原来这许许多多注释文字，每一句都在故意导人误入歧途。可是参研图谱之人，又有那一个肯不去钻研注解？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 569,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "岛主你说那许多字都是没用的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 571,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "非但无用，而且大大有害。倘若没这些注解，我二人的无数心血，又何至尽数虚耗……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 571,
      "line_end": 575
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "原来这篇《太玄经》也不是真的蝌蚪文，只不过……只不过是一些经脉穴道的线路方位而已。唉，四十年的光阴，四十年的光阴！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 577,
      "line_end": 581
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "text": "白首太玄经！兄弟，你的头发也真雪白了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 581,
      "line_end": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "他在石壁上故意写上这许多字，教人走上错路，那是为了什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 587,
      "line_end": 589
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "到底是什么居心，那就难说得很了。这位武林前辈或许不愿后人得之太易，又或者这些注释是后来另外有人加上去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 589,
      "line_end": 593
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "或许这位武林前辈不喜读书人，故意布下圈套，好令像石帮主这样不识字的忠厚老实之人得益。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 595,
      "line_end": 597
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "text": "这位前辈用心深刻，又有谁推想得出？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 599
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "二位岛主，倘若我学到的功夫确实有用，自当尽数向两位说知。咱们这就去第一座石室之中，我一一说来，我……我……我决不敢有丝毫隐瞒。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 601,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "小兄弟的好意，我二人心领了。小兄弟宅心仁厚，该受此益，日后领袖武林群伦，造福苍生，自非鲜浅。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 607,
      "line_end": 611
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "正是，图谱之谜既已解破，我二人心愿已了。是小兄弟练成，还是我二人练成，那也都是一样。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 611,
      "line_end": 613
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "那么我把这些小蝌蚪详详细细说给两位听，好不好？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 615,
      "line_end": 615
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "神功既得传人，这壁上的图谱也该功成身退了。小兄弟，你再瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 617,
      "line_end": 619
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "怎……怎么会这样？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 623,
      "line_end": 625
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "小兄弟适才……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 627,
      "line_end": 627
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "木岛主",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "此事慢慢再说，咱们且去聚会众人，宣布此事如何？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 627,
      "line_end": 629
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "甚好，甚好。石帮主，请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 629,
      "line_end": 631
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "小兄弟，适才石室中的事情，你千万不可向旁人说起。就算是你最亲近之人，也不能让他得知你已解明石壁上的武功秘奥，否则你一生之中将有无穷祸患，无穷烦恼。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 663,
      "line_end": 667
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "是，谨遵岛主吩咐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 667,
      "line_end": 667
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "常言道：慢藏诲盗……因此这件事说什么也不能泄露了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 669,
      "line_end": 675
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "是，多谢岛主指点，晚辈感激不尽。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 675,
      "line_end": 677
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "可惜我和木兄弟不能见你大展奇才，扬威江湖了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 679,
      "line_end": 679
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_qun_xiong",
      "text": "众位朋友，咱们在这岛上相聚，总算是一番缘法。时至今日，大伙儿缘份已尽，这可要分手了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 687,
      "line_end": 689
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "群雄",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 691,
      "line_end": 693
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "群雄",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "岛上出了什么事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 691,
      "line_end": 693
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "群雄",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "两位岛主有何见教？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 691,
      "line_end": 693
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "群雄",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "两位岛主要离岛远行吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 693,
      "line_end": 693
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_qun_xiong",
      "text": "各位，咱们在此相聚，只盼能解破这首“侠客行”武学图解的秘奥，可惜时不我予，这座侠客岛转眼便要陆沉了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 699,
      "line_end": 701
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "群雄",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 703,
      "line_end": 705
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "群雄",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "是地震么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 703,
      "line_end": 705
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "群雄",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "火山爆发？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 703,
      "line_end": 705
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "群雄",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "岛主如何得知？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 705,
      "line_end": 705
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_qun_xiong",
      "text": "适才我和木兄弟发见本岛中心即将有火山喷发，这一发作，全岛立时化为火海。此刻雷声隐隐，大害将作，各位急速离去罢。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 705,
      "line_end": 709
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "龙岛主",
      "listener": "char_qun_xiong",
      "text": "各位如果不信，不妨去石室一观，各室俱已震坍，石壁已毁，便地震不起，火山不喷，留在此间也无事可为了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 711,
      "line_end": 713
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_long_dao_zhu",
      "text": "龙岛主、木岛主，你……你们怎么了？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 729,
      "line_end": 729
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_zhang_san",
      "text": "两位岛主本来好端端地，怎么……怎么便死了？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 731,
      "line_end": 733
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_san",
      "speaker_name": "张三",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "两位师父逝世之时，说道他二人大愿得偿，虽离人世，心中……却感满足，十分平安喜乐。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 733,
      "line_end": 735
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_da_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫大弟子",
      "listener": "char_qun_xiong",
      "text": "众位嘉宾，我等恩师去世之前，遗命请各位急速离岛。各位以前所得的“赏善罚恶”铜牌，日后或仍有用，请勿随意丢弃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 741,
      "line_end": 745
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_da_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫大弟子",
      "listener": "char_qun_xiong",
      "text": "他日各位若有为难之事，持牌到南海之滨的小渔村中相洽，我等兄弟或可相助一臂之力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 745,
      "line_end": 747
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_shan_da_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青衫大弟子",
      "listener": "char_qun_xiong",
      "text": "海边船只已备，各位便请动程。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 751,
      "line_end": 751
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_san",
      "speaker_name": "张三",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "兄弟，你这就去罢，日后我们当来探你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 753,
      "line_end": 755
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李四",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "三弟，我们恩师吩咐，以后要当你是侠客岛的自己人一般相待。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 757,
      "line_end": 759
    }
  ],
